    "body" : "<p>Yes,  a Java <code>Map</code> can have any types of keys or values.</p>\n\n<p>What you probably want here is a <code>Map&lt;String, Set&lt;String&gt;&gt;</code> (since I assume a channel cannot have the same member twice, right?).</p>\n\n<p>And any really means any: you may even have <code>Map</code>s as keys to <code>Map</code>s.</p>\n"
