  "title" : "Data structure to hold paired values",
  "body" : "<p>This is what I am trying to do :</p>\n\n<p>Having a list of channel names where each channel name has several members. Both are Strings.</p>\n\n<p>What I am doing now is having a 2d ArrayList.First value on each ArrayList is the channel name and next are its members. Is there a better way to do this (without creating classes) ? </p>\n\n<p>Can a Map have many values for one key ? So that I have a channel as Key and members as Values to that Key ?</p>\n\n<p>Thanks !</p>\n"
}